{"title":"2020-07-03","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><p>NHK の女子アナ、桑子アナの次のスターダムにのし上がってるのは和久田麻由子アナなのかな。東大卒。</p>\n<p>最近けっこう見かけるなぁ。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>ピカチュウがww</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-03/20200703-092316-Screenshot_20200703-092316.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-03/20200703-092316-Screenshot_20200703-092316.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-03/20200703-092323-Screenshot_20200703-092323.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-03/20200703-092323-Screenshot_20200703-092323.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>イオンかほく、すいてる時間に久々に中を歩いてみたけど、閉店セールとか 50% オフとかがちらほら…</p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記,つぶやき,雑記帳","updated":"2020-07-04T08:57:14","published":"2020-07-04T08:57:14"}